headline: Everyday Care in Action: Thousands of Kenvue Employees Come Together Across 21 Markets to Help Advance Healthier Communities
summary: SUMMIT, N.J., May 14, 2025--Kenvue Inc. today announced its global efforts in celebration of Kenvue Cares Week, the company’s signature annual volunteer initiative.
